quran[182]{c,v,t}:
  37,1,(Allāhu búra pẹ̀lú) àwọn mọlāika olùtò-lọ́wọ̀ọ̀wọ́ tààrà
  37,2,àti àwọn mọlāika t’ó ń wọ́ ẹ̀ṣújò kiri tààrà
  37,3,àti àwọn mọlāika òǹké-tírà ìrántí
  37,4,"Dájúdájú Ọlọ́hun yín, Ọ̀kan ṣoṣo ni"
  37,5,Olúwa àwọn sánmọ̀ àti ilẹ̀ àti ohunkóhun tí ń bẹ láààrin àwọn méjèèjì. Òun sì ni Olúwa àwọn ibùyọ òòrùn
  37,6,Dájúdájú Àwa fi àwọn ìràwọ̀ ṣe sánmọ̀ ilé ayé ní ọ̀ṣọ́
  37,7,àti ìṣọ́ níbi (aburú) gbogbo èṣù olóríkunkun
  37,8,(Àwọn èṣù) kò sì níí lè tẹ́tí sí ìjọ (mọlāika t’ó wà ní) àyè gíga jùlọ (nínú sánmọ̀). (Àwọn mọlāika) yó sì máa ku (àwọn èṣù) lókò (ẹ̀ta ìràwọ̀) ní gbogbo agbègbè (sánmọ̀)
  37,9,Wọ́n ń lé wọn dànù. Ìyà àìlópin sì wà fún wọn
  37,10,"(Wọn kò níí gbọ́ ọ̀rọ̀ ní kíkún) àyàfi ẹni tí ó bá rí ọ̀rọ̀ àjígbọ́ gbé, nígbà náà (ni mọlāika) yó sì fi ẹ̀ta ìràwọ̀ iná t’ó máa jó o tẹ̀lé e"
  37,11,Bi wọ́n léèrè wò pé ṣé àwọn ni ìṣẹ̀dá wọn lágbára jùlọ ni tàbí àwọn (ènìyàn) tí A dá? Dájúdájú Àwa dá wọn láti ara erùpẹ̀ t’ó lẹ̀ mọ́ra wọn
  37,12,"Rárá (kò jọra wọn); ìwọ ṣèèmọ̀ (nípa al-Ƙur’ān), àwọn sì ń ṣe yẹ̀yẹ́"
  37,13,"Àti pé nígbà tí wọ́n bá ṣe ìrántí fún wọn, wọn kò níí lo ìrántí"
  37,14,"Nígbà tí wọ́n bá tún rí àmì kan, wọn yóò máa ṣe yẹ̀yẹ́"
  37,15,"Wọ́n sì wí pé: \"Èyí kò jẹ́ kiní kan bí kò ṣe idán pọ́nńbélé"
  37,16,"Ṣé nígbà tí a bá kú tán, tí a ti di erùpẹ̀ àti egungun, ṣé dájúdájú Wọn yóò tún gbé wa dìde ni"
  37,17,"Ṣé àti àwọn bàbá wa, àwọn ẹni àkọ́kọ́"
  37,18,"Sọ pé: \"Bẹ́ẹ̀ ni. Ẹ̀yin yó sì di ẹni yẹpẹrẹ"
  37,19,"Nítorí náà, igbe ẹyọ kan mà ni. Nígbà náà ni wọn yóò máa wò sùn"
  37,20,"Wọ́n á wí pé: \"Ègbé wa! Èyí ni Ọjọ́ ẹ̀san"
  37,21,Èyí ni ọjọ́ Ìdájọ́ èyí tí ẹ̀ ń pè nírọ́
  37,22,"Ẹ kó àwọn t’ó ṣàbòsí jọ, àwọn ìyàwó wọn àti ohun tí wọ́n ń jọ́sìn fún"
  37,23,lẹ́yìn Allāhu. Kí ẹ sì júwe wọn sí ojú ọ̀nà iná Jẹhīm
  37,24,"Ẹ dá wọn dúró ná, dájúdájú wọ́n máa bi wọ́n léèrè ìbéèrè"
  37,25,Kí ni kò jẹ́ kí ẹ ranra yín lọ́wọ́
  37,26,"Rárá, wọ́n ti juwọ́ jusẹ̀ sílẹ̀ ní òní ni"
  37,27,"Apá kan wọn yóò dojú kọ apá kan, tí wọn yóò máa bira wọn léèrè ìbéèrè"
  37,28,"(Àwọn ènìyàn) wí pé: \"Dájúdájú ẹ̀yin l’ẹ̀ ń gba ọ̀tún wọlé sí wa lára (láti ṣì wá lọ́nà)"
  37,29,"(Àwọn àlùjànnú) wí pé: \"Rárá o (àwa kọ́), ẹ̀yin ni ẹ kò jẹ́ onígbàgbọ́ òdodo"
  37,30,"Àti pé àwa kò ní agbára kan lórí yín, ṣùgbọ́n ẹ̀yin jẹ́ ìjọ olùtayọ-ẹnu àlà"
  37,31,Ọ̀rọ̀ Olúwa wa sì kò lé wa lórí pé dájúdájú àwa yóò tọ́ Iná wò
  37,32,"Nítorí náà, a ṣì yín lọ́nà. Dájúdájú àwa náà sì jẹ́ olùṣìnà"
  37,33,"Dájúdájú ní ọjọ́ yẹn, akẹgbẹ́ ni wọ́n nínú Ìyà"
  37,34,Dájúdájú báyẹn ni Àwa yóò ti ṣe pẹ̀lú àwọn ẹlẹ́ṣẹ̀
  37,35,"Dájúdájú nígbà tí wọ́n bá sọ fún wọn pé \"Kò sí ọlọ́hun tí ìjọ́sìn tọ́ sí àfi Allāhu.\", wọn yóò máa ṣègbéraga"
  37,36,"Wọ́n sì ń wí pé: \"Ṣé a máa fi àwọn òrìṣà wa sílẹ̀ nítorí eléwì wèrè kan"
  37,37,Kò rí bẹ́ẹ̀. Ó mú òdodo wá ni. Ó sì ń jẹ́rìí sí òdodo àwọn Òjíṣẹ́ náà
  37,38,Dájúdájú ẹ máa tọ́ ìyà ẹlẹ́ta-eléro wò
  37,39,A ò níí san yín ní ẹ̀san kan àfi ohun tí ẹ̀ ń ṣe níṣẹ́
  37,40,"Àfi àwọn ẹrúsìn Allāhu, àwọn ẹni ẹ̀ṣà"
  37,41,Ti àwọn wọ̀nyẹn sì ni arísìkí tí wọ́n ti mọ̀
  37,42,àwọn èso. Àwọn sì ni alápọ̀n-ọ́nlé
  37,43,nínú àwọn Ọgbà Ìdẹ̀ra
  37,44,Lórí àwọn ìtẹ́ ni wọn yóò ti kọjú síra wọn
  37,45,Wọn yóò máa gbé ife ọtí mímọ́ káà kiri ọ̀dọ̀ wọn
  37,46,Funfun ni (ọtí náà). Ó ń dùn lẹ́nu àwọn t’ó máa mu ún
  37,47,"Kò sí ìpalára kan fún wọn nínú rẹ̀, wọn kò sì níí hunrírà lórí rẹ̀"
  37,48,"Àwọn obìnrin tí kì í wo ẹlòmíìràn, àwọn ẹlẹ́yinjú ẹgẹ́ yó sì wà lọ́dọ̀ wọn"
  37,49,Wọ́n dà bí tinú ẹyin. ó tún jẹ́ kí á mọ̀ pé wọn kò retí ìkẹ́ kan kan lọ́run ní tiwọn. Tí ó bá jẹ́ pé wọ́n ń retí ìkẹ́ kan ní ọ̀run
  37,50,"Apá kan wọn yóò dojú kọ apá kan, tí wọn yóò máa bira wọn léèrè ìbéèrè"
  37,51,"Òǹsọ̀rọ̀ kan nínú wọn yóò sọ pé: \"Dájúdájú èmi ní ọ̀rẹ́ kan"
  37,52,"tí ó ń wí pé, “Ṣé dájúdájú ìwọ wà nínú àwọn onígbàgbọ́ nínú Ọjọ́ Àjíǹde"
  37,53,"Ṣé nígbà tí a bá kú tán, tí a ti di erùpẹ̀ àti egungun, ṣé dájúdájú Wọn yóò san wá ní ẹ̀san ni?”"
  37,54,"Ó sọ pé: \"Ṣé ẹ̀yin yóò yọjú wo (ẹni náà tí kò gbàgbọ́ nínú Ọjọ́ àjíǹde)"
  37,55,Ó yọjú wò ó. Ó sì rí i láààrin gbùngbùn nínú iná Jẹhīm
  37,56,"Ó (sì) sọ pé: \"Mó fi Allāhu búra, ìwọ fẹ́ẹ̀ kó ìparun bá mi tán"
  37,57,"Àti pé tí kì í bá ṣe ìdẹ̀ra Olúwa mi ni, èmi náà ìbá wà nínú ẹni tí wọ́n máa mú wá sínú Iná"
  37,58,Àwa kò sá níí kú mọ́ báyìí
  37,59,Àfi ikú wa àkọ́kọ́. Wọn kò sì níí jẹ àwa níyà
  37,60,"Dájúdájú èyí, òhun ni èrèǹjẹ ńlá"
  37,61,"Nítorí irú èyí, kí àwọn olùṣẹ̀sìn máa ṣẹ̀sìn lọ"
  37,62,Ǹjẹ́ ìyẹn l’ó lóore jùlọ ní ibùdésí ni tàbí igi zaƙūm (igi ẹlẹ́gùn-ún)
  37,63,Dájúdájú Àwa ṣe é ní àdánwò fún àwọn alábòsí
  37,64,Dájúdájú òhun ni igi kan tí ó máa hù jáde láti ìdí iná Jẹhīm
  37,65,Èso rẹ̀ dà bí orí àwọn èṣù
  37,66,"Dájúdájú wọn yóò máa jẹ nínú rẹ̀. Nítorí náà, wọn yóò fi kún inú wọn bámúbámú"
  37,67,"Lẹ́yìn náà, dájúdájú wọn yóò mu n̄ǹkan mímu àwọyúnwẹ̀jẹ̀ gbígbóná lé e lórí"
  37,68,"Lẹ́yìn náà, dájúdájú ibùpadàsí wọn ni iná Jẹhīm"
  37,69,Dájúdájú wọ́n bá àwọn bàbá wọn ní olùṣìnà
  37,70,Àwọn náà sì ń yára tẹ̀lé orípa wọn
  37,71,Dájúdájú ọ̀pọ̀lọ́pọ̀ àwọn ẹni àkọ́kọ́ ti ṣìnà ṣíwájú wọn
  37,72,Dájúdájú A ti rán àwọn olùkìlọ̀ sí wọn
  37,73,"Nítorí náà, wo bí àtubọ̀tán àwọn ẹni-akìlọ̀-fún ti rí"
  37,74,"Àfi àwọn ẹrúsìn Allāhu, àwọn ẹni ẹ̀ṣà"
  37,75,Dájúdájú (Ànábì) Nūh pè Wá. A sì dára ní olùjẹ́pè
  37,76,A gba òun àti àwọn ará ilé rẹ̀ là kúrò nínú ìbànújẹ́ ńlá
  37,77,A dá àwọn àrọ́mọdọ́mọ rẹ̀ sí lẹ́yìn rẹ̀
  37,78,A sì fún un ní orúkọ rere láààrin àwọn ẹni ìkẹ́yìn
  37,79,Àlàáfíà kí ó máa bá (Ànábì) Nūh láààrin gbogbo ẹ̀dá
  37,80,Dájúdájú báyẹn ni Àwa ṣe ń san àwọn olùṣe-rere ní ẹ̀san (rere)
  37,81,"Dájúdájú òun wà nínú àwọn ẹrúsìn Wa, àwọn onígbàgbọ́ òdodo"
  37,82,"Lẹ́yìn náà, A tẹ àwọn yòókù rì sínú agbami"
  37,83,Dájúdájú (Ànábì) ’Ibrọ̄hīm wà nínú ìjọ (tí ó tẹ̀lé ìlànà) rẹ̀
  37,84,(Ẹ rántí) nígbà tí òun náà dojú kọ Olúwa rẹ̀ pẹ̀lú ọkàn mímọ́
  37,85,"(Rántí) nígbà tí ó sọ fún bàbá rẹ̀ àti àwọn ènìyàn rẹ̀ pé: \"Kí ni ẹ̀ ń jọ́sìn fún"
  37,86,Ṣé ẹ̀ ń gbèrò láti sọ irọ́ di ọlọ́hun lẹ́yìn Allāhu
  37,87,Kí sì ni èrò ọkàn yín sí Olúwa gbogbo ẹ̀dá?”
  37,88,Ó ṣíjú wo àwọn ìràwọ̀ gan-an
  37,89,"Ó sì sọ pé: \"Dájúdájú ó rẹ̀ mí"
  37,90,"Nítorí náà, wọ́n pa á tì, wọ́n sì lọ"
  37,91,"Nígbà náà, ó lọ sí ọ̀dọ̀ àwọn òrìṣà wọn. Ó sì sọ pé: \"Ṣé ẹ ò níí jẹun ni"
  37,92,Kí ni ó ṣe yín tí ẹ ò sọ̀rọ̀
  37,93,"Nígbà náà, ó dojú lílù kọ wọ́n pẹ̀lú ọwọ́ ọ̀tún (ó sì rún wọn wómúwómú)"
  37,94,(Àwọn abọ̀rìṣà) sáré wá dojú kọ ọ́
  37,95,"Ó sọ pé: \"Ṣé ẹ óò máa jọ́sìn fún n̄ǹkan tí ẹ gbẹ́ kalẹ̀ lére ni"
  37,96,Allāhu l’Ó sì dá ẹ̀yin àti n̄ǹkan tí ẹ̀ ń ṣe níṣẹ́
  37,97,"Wọ́n wí pé: \"Ẹ mọ ilé kan fún un, kí ẹ sì jù ú sínú iná"
  37,98,Wọ́n gbèrò ète sí i. A sì sọ wọ́n di ẹni yẹpẹrẹ
  37,99,"Ó sọ pé: \"Dájúdájú mo máa lọ sí (ìlú tí) Olúwa mi (pa mí láṣẹ láti lọ). Ó sì máa tọ́ mi sọ́nà (láti dé ibẹ̀)"
  37,100,"Olúwa mi, ta mí lọ́rẹ ọmọ nínú àwọn ẹni rere"
  37,101,A sì fún un ní ìró ìdùnnú (nípa bíbí) ọmọkùnrin aláfaradà
  37,102,"Nígbà tí (ọmọ náà) dàgbà, tí ó tó bá (bàbá rẹ̀) ṣe iṣẹ́, (bàbá rẹ̀) sọ pé: \"Ọmọ mi, dájúdájú èmi lá àlá pé dájúdájú mò ń dúńbú rẹ. Nítorí náà, wòye sí i, kí ni o rí sí i.\" Ó sọ pé: \"Bàbá mi, ṣe ohun tí Wọ́n pa láṣẹ fún ọ. O máa bá mi nínú àwọn onísùúrù, tí Allāhu bá fẹ́"
  37,103,"Nígbà tí àwọn méjèèjì juwọ́ jusẹ̀ sílẹ̀, tí (Ànábì ’Ibrọ̄hīm) sì dojú (ọmọ) rẹ̀ bolẹ̀"
  37,104,"A pè é (báyìí) pé, ’Ibrọ̄hīm"
  37,105,o kúkú ti mú àlá náà ṣẹ. Dájúdájú báyẹn ni Àwa ṣe ń san àwọn olùṣe-rere ní ẹ̀san (rere)
  37,106,"Dájúdájú èyí, òhun ni àdánwò pọ́nńbélé"
  37,107,A sì fi àgbò ńlá ṣèràpadà rẹ̀
  37,108,A tún fún un ní orúkọ rere láààrin àwọn ẹni ìkẹ́yìn
  37,109,Àlàáfíà kí ó máa bá (Ànábì) ’Ibrọ̄hīm
  37,110,Báyẹn ni A ṣe ń san àwọn olùṣe-rere ní ẹ̀san (rere)
  37,111,"Dájúdájú ó wà nínú àwọn ẹrúsìn Wa, àwọn onígbàgbọ́ òdodo"
  37,112,"A tún fún un ní ìró ìdùnnú (nípa bíbí) ’Ishāƙ, (ó máa jẹ́) Ànábì. (Ó sì máa wà) nínú àwọn ẹni rere"
  37,113,Àti pé A fún òun àti ’Ishāƙ ní ìbùkún. Ẹni rere àti alábòsí pọ́nńbélé (t’ó ń ṣàbòsí sí) ẹ̀mí ara rẹ̀ wà nínú àrọ́mọdọ́mọ àwọn méjèèjì
  37,114,Dájúdájú A ṣoore fún (Ànábì) Mūsā àti Hārūn
  37,115,A gba àwọn méjèèjì àti ìjọ àwọn méjèèjì là kúrò nínú ìbànújẹ́ ńlá
  37,116,A tún ṣàrànṣe fún wọn. Àwọn ni wọ́n jẹ́ olùborí (ọ̀tá wọn)
  37,117,A sì fún àwọn méjèèjì ní Tírà t’ó yanjú
  37,118,A tún fi àwọn méjèèjì mọ̀nà tààrà
  37,119,A fún àwọn méjèèjì ní orúkọ rere láààrin àwọn ẹni ìkẹ́yìn
  37,120,Àlàáfíà kí ó máa bá (Ànábì) Mūsā àti Hārūn
  37,121,Dájúdájú báyẹn ni Àwa ṣe ń san àwọn olùṣe-rere ní ẹ̀san (rere)
  37,122,"Dájúdájú àwọn méjèèjì wà nínú àwọn ẹrúsìn Wa, àwọn onígbàgbọ́ òdodo"
  37,123,Dájúdájú (Ànábì) ’Ilyās wà nínú àwọn Òjíṣẹ́
  37,124,"(Ẹ rántí) nígbà tí ó sọ fún ìjọ rẹ̀ pé: \"Ṣé ẹ ò níí bẹ̀rù Allāhu ni"
  37,125,"Ṣé ẹ óò máa pe òrìṣà kan, ẹ sì máa fi Ẹni t’Ó dára jùlọ nínú àwọn ẹlẹ́dàá sílẹ̀, وَهُوَ خَيْرُ ٱلْحَٰكِمِينَ Òun l’Ó sì dára jùlọ nínú àwọn olùdájọ́. (sūrah al-’A‘rọ̄f 7:87) وَهُوَ أَسْرَعُ ٱلْحَٰسِبِينَ Òun sì yára jùlọ nínú àwọn oníṣirò. (sūrah al-’Ani‘ām 6:62) olùdájọ́ aláàánú ìbáà mọ bíi ọmọ iná igún àfi kí Allāhu jẹ́ Ẹlẹ́dàá rẹ̀. Kódà àdámọ́ owó àti okòwò tí wọ́n sọ di “ọrọ̀-Ajé. Àwọn t’ó ń bọ́ ẹlòmíìràn náà ń sọra wọn di olùpèsè. Yàtọ̀ sí pé Allāhu ti fi rinlẹ̀ pé Òun nìkan ni Olùpèsè fún gbogbo ẹ̀dá Rẹ̀. Tí èyí kò bá tí ì dá àwọn kan lójú bẹ́ẹ̀ tí wọ́n sì fẹ́ gbé gbogbo ìpèsè olúkùlùkù lórí ìwọ̀n nínú àánú tí Allāhu fi sí àwọn ẹ̀dá kan lọ́kàn ni wọ́n fi di aláàánú. Nítorí náà Allāhu ni Aláàánú jùlọ nínú àwọn aláàánú"
  37,126,"(ẹ̀ ń fi) Allāhu (sílẹ̀), Olúwa yín àti Olúwa àwọn bàbá yín, àwọn ẹni àkọ́kọ́"
  37,127,"Wọ́n sì pè é ní òpùrọ́. Nítorí náà, wọ́n máa mú wọn wá sínú Iná"
  37,128,"Àfi àwọn ẹrúsìn Allāhu, àwọn ẹni ẹ̀ṣà"
  37,129,A fún un ní orúkọ rere láààrin àwọn ẹni ìkẹ́yìn
  37,130,Àlàáfíà kí ó máa bá (Ànábì) ’Ilyās
  37,131,Dájúdájú báyẹn ni Àwa ṣe ń san àwọn olùṣe-rere ní ẹ̀san (rere)
  37,132,"Dájúdájú ó wà nínú àwọn ẹrúsìn Wa, àwọn onígbàgbọ́ òdodo"
  37,133,Dájúdájú (Ànábì) Lūt wà nínú àwọn Òjíṣẹ́
  37,134,(Ẹ rántí) nígbà tí A gba òun àti gbogbo àwọn ará ilé rẹ̀ là
  37,135,Àyàfi arúgbóbìnrin kan tí ó wà nínú àwọn t’ó ṣẹ́ kù lẹ́yìn (láààrin àwọn tí A parẹ́)
  37,136,"Lẹ́yìn náà, A pa àwọn yòókù run"
  37,137,Dájúdájú ẹ̀yin náà kúkú ń gba ọ̀dọ̀ wọn kọjá láàárọ̀-láàárọ̀
  37,138,àti ní alaalẹ́. Ṣé ẹ ò níí ṣe làákàyè ni
  37,139,Dájúdájú (Ànábì) Yūnus kúkú wà nínú àwọn Òjíṣẹ́
  37,140,(Ẹ rántí) nígbà tí ó sá lọ sínú ọkọ̀ ojú-omi t’ó kún kẹ́kẹ́
  37,141,Ó sì bá wọn muje pọ̀. Ó sì wà nínú àwọn tí aje ṣí mọ́ lórí
  37,142,"Nítorí náà, ẹja gbé e mì; ó sì ń dá ara rẹ̀ lẹ́bi"
  37,143,"Nítorí náà, tí kò bá jẹ́ pé ó wà nínú àwọn olùṣàfọ̀mọ́ fún Allāhu"
  37,144,dájúdájú ìbá wà nínú ẹja títí di ọjọ́ tí wọn yóò gbé ẹ̀dá dìde
  37,145,"Nítorí náà, A jù ú sí orí ilẹ́ gban̄sasa létí omi. Ó sì jẹ́ aláìlera"
  37,146,A sì mú igi Yẹƙtīn hù jáde láti ṣíji bò ó
  37,147,A tún rán an níṣẹ́ sí ọ̀kẹ́ márùn-ún (ènìyàn) tàbí kí wọ́n lékún sí i
  37,148,Wọ́n gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo. A sì fún wọn ní ìgbádùn títí di ìgbà díẹ̀
  37,149,"Bi wọ́n léèrè wò pé: \"Ṣé Olúwa rẹ l’ó ni àwọn ọmọbìnrin, tiwọn sì ni ọmọkùnrin"
  37,150,"Tàbí A dá àwọn mọlāika ní obìnrin, tí àwọn sì jẹ́ ẹlẹ́rìí"
  37,151,"Gbọ́, nínú irọ́ wọn ni pé dájúdájú wọ́n ń wí pé"
  37,152,"Allāhu bímọ.\" Dájúdájú òpùrọ́ ni wọ́n"
  37,153,Ṣé (Allāhu) ṣẹ̀ṣà àwọn ọmọbìnrin lórí àwọn ọmọkùnrin ni
  37,154,Kí l’ó ń ṣe yín tí ẹ fi ń dájọ́ báyìí
  37,155,Ṣé ẹ ò níí lo ìrántí ni
  37,156,Tàbí ẹ ní ẹ̀rí t’ó yanjú lọ́wọ́ ni
  37,157,Ẹ mú tírà yín wà nígbà náà tí ẹ bá jẹ́ olódodo
  37,158,Wọ́n tún fi ìbátan sáààrin (Allāhu) àti àlùjànnú! Àwọn àlùjànnú sì ti mọ̀ pé dájúdájú wọ́n kúkú máa mú àwọn wá sínú Iná ni
  37,159,Mímọ́ ni fún Allāhu tayọ ohun tí wọ́n ń fi ròyìn (Rẹ̀)
  37,160,"Àfi àwọn ẹrúsìn Allāhu, àwọn ẹni ẹ̀ṣà"
  37,161,Dájúdájú ẹ̀yin àti n̄ǹkan tí ẹ̀ ń jọ́sìn fún (lẹ́yìn Allāhu)
  37,162,ẹ ò lè fi ṣi ẹnì kan kan lọ́nà
  37,163,àfi ẹni tí ó bá fẹ́ wọ inú iná Jẹhīm
  37,164,Kò sí ẹnì kan nínú àwa (mọlāika) àfi kí ó ní ibùdúró tí wọ́n ti mọ̀
  37,165,"Dájúdájú àwa, a kúkú wà ní ọ̀wọ̀ọ̀wọ́"
  37,166,"Àti pé dájúdájú àwa, àwa kúkú ni olùṣàfọ̀mọ́ (fún Allāhu)"
  37,167,Wọ́n kúkú ń wí pé
  37,168,Tí ó bá jẹ́ pé dájúdájú a bá ní (tírà) ìrántí kan nínú (àwọn tírà) àwọn ẹni àkọ́kọ́
  37,169,"dájúdájú àwa ìbá jẹ́ ẹrúsìn Allāhu, àwọn ẹni ẹ̀ṣà"
  37,170,Ṣùgbọ́n wọ́n ṣàì gbàgbọ́ nínú (Allāhu). Láìpẹ́ wọ́n máa mọ̀
  37,171,"Dájúdájú ọ̀rọ̀ Wa ti ṣíwájú fún àwọn ẹrúsìn Wa, àwọn Òjíṣẹ́"
  37,172,"Dájúdájú àwọn, àwọn l’a kúkú máa ṣàrànṣe fún"
  37,173,"Àti pé dájúdájú àwọn ọmọ ogun Wa, àwọn kúkú ni olùborí"
  37,174,"Nítorí náà, ṣẹ́rí kúrò lọ́dọ̀ wọn fún ìgbà díẹ̀"
  37,175,"Àti pé máa wò wọ́n níran ná, àwọn náà ń bọ̀ wá ríran wò"
  37,176,Ṣé ìyà Wa ni wọ́n ń wá pẹ̀lú ìkánjú
  37,177,"Nígbà tí ó bá sọ̀kalẹ̀ sí agboolé wọn, òwúrọ̀ ọjọ́ náà yó sì burú fún àwọn ẹni-akìlọ̀-fún"
  37,178,Kúrò lọ́dọ̀ wọn títí di ìgbà kan ná
  37,179,"Àti pé máa wò wọ́n níran ná, àwọn náà ń bọ̀ wá ríran wò"
  37,180,"Mímọ́ ni fún Olúwa rẹ, Olúwa agbára, tayọ ohun tí wọ́n ń fi ròyìn (Rẹ̀)"
  37,181,Kí àlàáfíà máa bá àwọn Òjíṣẹ́
  37,182,"Gbogbo ọpẹ́ ń jẹ́ ti Allāhu, Olúwa gbogbo ẹ̀dá"